item.name: Processes

query.description:
Mutliple status are allowed. Possible values are: 
PENDING
CREATED
IN_PROGRESS
STUCK
FINISHED
INCOMPLETE
CANCELED
The backend performs a full text search based on this field, that is, you can give a partial tenant id
Multiple refs are allowed, in form of an array
Multiple countries are allowed, in form of an array
Multiple facility countries are allowed, in form of an array
One or multiple values from the ServlceLevelEnum, such as SAMEDAY or DELIVERY, in form of an array
